results.description:
We offer cases for tons of devices. If your device is listed below in the description but not in the dropdown menu, select Unlisted. Then in the notes section, write the device you would like. Please message us with any inquiries you may have :-)

Our high quality phone cases are designed for impact. The 2 different styles we sell are TPU rubber silicone and 2-Piece Dual Layer.

TPU rubber silicone cases are our level one protection. Has a lip on the front to protect screen when laying face down.

2-Piece Dual Layer cases are made for high impact. Layer 1 is silicone rubber that slips into Layer 2, which is a hard outer shell. The result is the best protection for your phone.

•	Precisely cut openings provide full access to all ports & buttons
•	Protects screen when phone is laid face down. Case is raised around edges to protect screen from damage.
•	High Gloss TPU frames the screen.
•	Ultra Thin, lightweight and durable
•	Protects phone from dirt accumulation, scratches and chipping

Fitting the phone models from any carrier, our cases are a perfect stylish way to protect the back of your phone. Covering the back, sides, and corners of the phone, this case allows full access to all your ports and buttons. This is NOT an actual 3D case. It is a printed image on a case.

Protect the back of your phone with style and personality. Lightweight and offers a slim profile. Please note this case does not cover the front screen in any way.

PROCESS: Each item is embellished with my creative designs one at a time using a unique printing technique that allows me to permanently instill an image onto a thin aluminum insert that is placed on the back of the molded plastic case. The insert is heated using a unique print process, cooled and permanently adhered to the phone case. The result is a vibrant, permanent imprint that is smudge, scratch, water and fade resistant. 

PRODUCT CARE: Clean with a dry cloth or fabric. Feel free to use your fingers to wipe it down also (lol). Do NOT come into contact with keys or sharp objects (knives, razors, porcupines etc). Do NOT handle with alcohol liquids, liquid bleach or corrosive chemicals. (This may cause discoloration over extended periods).
